'''立陶宛文化'''結合了本土傳統，並受到北歐國家的文化影響。立陶宛的基督教傳統則是該國和[[波蘭|波蘭]]的歷史連結的影響。立陶宛的語言及文化和[[拉脫維亞|拉脫維亞]]相似。立陶宛有著波羅的海最單純的人口結構。據2001年人口普查，立陶宛有83.45%的人認為自己是立陶宛人，6.74%是波蘭人，6.31%是俄羅斯人，1.23%是白俄羅斯人，2.27%是其他 <ref name="censusethnic">{{cite web |url=http://www.stat.gov.lt/en/pages/view/?id=1731 |title=Population by Ethnicity |accessdate=2008-09-17 |publisher=Department of Statistics to the Government of the Republic of Lithuania |year=2005 }}</ref>。立陶宛的波蘭人集中在維爾紐斯地區<ref>{{cite news|first=Angelė |last=Vyšniauskaitė |title=LIETUVIŲ ETNINĖ KULTŪRA – AKCENTAS DAUGIALYPĖJE EUROPOS KULTŪROJE |year=2005 |publisher= |url=http://samogitia.mch.mii.lt/KULTURA/Seminaras_etnine_kultura.htm |work= |pages= |accessdate=2008-01-26 |language=lt |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080125230536/http://samogitia.mch.mii.lt/KULTURA/Seminaras_etnine_kultura.htm |archivedate=2008-01-25 }}</ref>。立陶宛的官方語言是立陶宛語，一些學者認為立陶宛語是最接近原始印歐語的語言<ref>{{cite book | last = Frucht | first = Richard | authorlink = | title = Eastern Europe: An Introduction to the People, Lands, and Culture | publisher = ABC-CLIO | year = 2005 | location = | pages = [https://archive.org/details/easterneuropeint00fruc/page/n209 188] | url =https://archive.org/details/easterneuropeint00fruc| doi = | id = | isbn = 1-57607-800-0 }}</ref>。立陶宛大多數人是天主教徒。據2001年普查，79%的立陶宛人是羅馬天主教徒<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stat.gov.lt/en/pages/view/?id=1734 |title=Population by Religious Confession |accessdate=2008-09-17 |publisher=Department of Statistics to the Government of the Republic of Lithuania |year=2005 }}</ref>。天主教在立陶宛抵抗蘇聯統治中發揮了重要作用。
